Instructions:

This is a Shell for Dielet ProgramFlows generation pymtpl.

1. For dielet module, please provide your updates as below:
   IP content in concurrent flow -> dielet_repo/POR_TP/Class_NVL_U8C/ProgramFlowsTestPlan/IP*_FLOWS.py
   PKG, Init or Fail Flow -> dielet_repo/POR_TP/Class_NVL_U8C/ProgramFlowsTestPlan/ProgramFlows*.py

2. For common module update:
   please provide your updates in Common repo central area ->
   dielet_repo/Shared/POR_TP/Class_NVL_U8C/ProgramFlowsTestPlan/ProgramFlowsSharedPKG.py

3. Please right-click this .runme file to trigger "Custom Commands" -> "Run GenPgmFlows Pymtpl".